      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        Which is ironic &mdash; I keep customer churn under 1%. The rest of the site is fully
        retained:
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.9rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &middot; <a href="/experience">Experience</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
